{
  "video_id": "lwVYaY39YbQ",
  "title": "How fake news does real harm | Stephanie Busari",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12892.0,
      "end_time": 15700.0,
      "text": "I want to tell you a story about a girl."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16335.0,
      "end_time": 18447.0,
      "text": "But I can&#39;t tell you her real name."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18835.0,
      "end_time": 20748.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s just call her Hadiza."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21381.0,
      "end_time": 22870.0,
      "text": "Hadiza is 20."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23459.0,
      "end_time": 24610.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s shy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24634.0,
      "end_time": 27868.0,
      "text": "but she has a beautiful smile that lights up her face."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28779.0,
      "end_time": 30709.0,
      "text": "But she&#39;s in constant pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32463.0,
      "end_time": 35937.0,
      "text": "And she will likely be on medication for the rest of her life."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36866.0,
      "end_time": 38371.0,
      "text": "Do you want to know why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39784.0,
      "end_time": 42641.0,
      "text": "Hadiza is a Chibok girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42665.0,
      "end_time": 45897.0,
      "text": "and on April 14, 2014, she was kidnapped"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45922.0,
      "end_time": 47546.0,
      "text": "by Boko Haram terrorists."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48290.0,
      "end_time": 50799.0,
      "text": "She managed to escape, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50823.0,
      "end_time": 54200.0,
      "text": "by jumping off the truck that was carrying the girls."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54440.0,
      "end_time": 57336.0,
      "text": "But when she landed, she broke both her legs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57361.0,
      "end_time": 60781.0,
      "text": "and she had to crawl on her tummy to hide in the bushes."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60805.0,
      "end_time": 64882.0,
      "text": "She told me she was terrified that Boko Haram would come back for her."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65524.0,
      "end_time": 70151.0,
      "text": "She was one of 57 girls who would escape by jumping off trucks that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70175.0,
      "end_time": 72716.0,
      "text": "This story, quite rightly, caused ripples"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 72740.0,
      "end_time": 74112.0,
      "text": "around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74136.0,
      "end_time": 77405.0,
      "text": "People like Michelle Obama, Malala and others"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77430.0,
      "end_time": 79522.0,
      "text": "lent their voices in protest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79546.0,
      "end_time": 82807.0,
      "text": "and at about the same time -- I was living in London at the time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82831.0,
      "end_time": 87474.0,
      "text": "I was sent from London to Abuja to cover the World Economic Forum"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87498.0,
      "end_time": 89920.0,
      "text": "that Nigeria was hosting for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90475.0,
      "end_time": 94538.0,
      "text": "But when we arrived, it was clear that there was only one story in town."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95729.0,
      "end_time": 97574.0,
      "text": "We put the government under pressure."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97598.0,
      "end_time": 100160.0,
      "text": "We asked tough questions about what they were doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100184.0,
      "end_time": 101675.0,
      "text": "to bring these girls back."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102199.0,
      "end_time": 103923.0,
      "text": "Understandably,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103947.0,
      "end_time": 106754.0,
      "text": "they weren&#39;t too happy with our line of questioning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106778.0,
      "end_time": 110527.0,
      "text": "and let&#39;s just say we received our fair share of \"alternative facts.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110551.0,
      "end_time": 113232.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113256.0,
      "end_time": 116454.0,
      "text": "Influential Nigerians were telling us at the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 116478.0,
      "end_time": 118475.0,
      "text": "that we were na√Øve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118499.0,
      "end_time": 121702.0,
      "text": "we didn&#39;t understand the political situation in Nigeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122720.0,
      "end_time": 124815.0,
      "text": "But they also told us"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 124839.0,
      "end_time": 127447.0,
      "text": "that the story of the Chibok girls"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 127471.0,
      "end_time": 128656.0,
      "text": "was a hoax."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 130850.0,
      "end_time": 132785.0,
      "text": "Sadly, this hoax narrative has persisted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132809.0,
      "end_time": 135990.0,
      "text": "and there are still people in Nigeria today"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 135123.0,
      "end_time": 137886.0,
      "text": "who believe that the Chibok girls were never kidnapped."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138751.0,
      "end_time": 141314.0,
      "text": "Yet I was talking to people like these --"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 142221.0,
      "end_time": 143926.0,
      "text": "devastated parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143950.0,
      "end_time": 148400.0,
      "text": "who told us that on the day Boko Haram kidnapped their daughters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 148280.0,
      "end_time": 152602.0,
      "text": "they ran into the Sambisa Forest after the trucks carrying their daughters."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 152626.0,
      "end_time": 156354.0,
      "text": "They were armed with machetes, but they were forced to turn back"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156378.0,
      "end_time": 158226.0,
      "text": "because Boko Haram had guns."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159165.0,
      "end_time": 162828.0,
      "text": "For two years, inevitably, the news agenda moved on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162852.0,
      "end_time": 164582.0,
      "text": "and for two years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164606.0,
      "end_time": 167765.0,
      "text": "we didn&#39;t hear much about the Chibok girls."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167789.0,
      "end_time": 169658.0,
      "text": "Everyone presumed they were dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170530.0,
      "end_time": 172400.0,
      "text": "But in April last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 172640.0,
      "end_time": 174269.0,
      "text": "I was able to obtain this video."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 174856.0,
      "end_time": 176596.0,
      "text": "This is a still from the video"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 176620.0,
      "end_time": 179734.0,
      "text": "that Boko Haram filmed as a proof of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 180743.0,
      "end_time": 183287.0,
      "text": "and through a source, I obtained this video."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 183929.0,
      "end_time": 185466.0,
      "text": "But before I could publish it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 185490.0,
      "end_time": 188515.0,
      "text": "I had to travel to the northeast of Nigeria"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 188539.0,
      "end_time": 190606.0,
      "text": "to talk to the parents, to verify it."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 191137.0,
      "end_time": 194514.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t have to wait too long for confirmation."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 195450.0,
      "end_time": 198780.0,
      "text": "One of the mothers, when she watched the video, told me"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 198804.0,
      "end_time": 201504.0,
      "text": "that if she could have reached into the laptop"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 201528.0,
      "end_time": 205547.0,
      "text": "and pulled our her child from the laptop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 205571.0,
      "end_time": 206977.0,
      "text": "she would have done so."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 208230.0,
      "end_time": 211245.0,
      "text": "For those of you who are parents, like myself, in the audience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 211269.0,
      "end_time": 214970.0,
      "text": "you can only imagine the anguish"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 214121.0,
      "end_time": 215580.0,
      "text": "that that mother felt."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 217421.0,
      "end_time": 223975.0,
      "text": "This video would go on to kick-start negotiation talks with Boko Haram."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 223999.0,
      "end_time": 227966.0,
      "text": "And a Nigerian senator told me that because of this video"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 227991.0,
      "end_time": 229984.0,
      "text": "they entered into those talks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 230800.0,
      "end_time": 233514.0,
      "text": "because they had long presumed that the Chibok girls were dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 234459.0,
      "end_time": 239161.0,
      "text": "Twenty-one girls were freed in October last year."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 239185.0,
      "end_time": 242753.0,
      "text": "Sadly, nearly 200 of them still remain missing."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 243511.0,
      "end_time": 247708.0,
      "text": "I must confess that I have not been a dispassionate observer"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 247732.0,
      "end_time": 248918.0,
      "text": "covering this story."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 248942.0,
      "end_time": 252750.0,
      "text": "I am furious when I think about the wasted opportunities"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 254520.0,
      "end_time": 255241.0,
      "text": "to rescue these girls."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 255265.0,
      "end_time": 259164.0,
      "text": "I am furious when I think about what the parents have told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 259189.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261963.00000000003,
      "text": "that if these were daughters of the rich and the powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 261987.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264148.0,
      "text": "they would have been found much earlier."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 266101.0,
      "end_time": 268109.0,
      "text": "And I am furious"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 268133.0,
      "end_time": 270610.0,
      "text": "that the hoax narrative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 270850.0,
      "end_time": 271962.0,
      "text": "I firmly believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 271987.0,
      "end_time": 274990.0,
      "text": "caused a delay;"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 274123.0,
      "end_time": 277111.0,
      "text": "it was part of the reason for the delay in their return."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 278500.0,
      "end_time": 283150.0,
      "text": "This illustrates to me the deadly danger of fake news."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 283390.0,
      "end_time": 284631.0,
      "text": "So what can we do about it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 285703.0,
      "end_time": 287619.0,
      "text": "There are some very smart people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 287644.0,
      "end_time": 290103.0,
      "text": "smart engineers at Google and Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 290127.0,
      "end_time": 295192.0,
      "text": "who are trying to use technology to stop the spread of fake news."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 295216.0,
      "end_time": 299967.0,
      "text": "But beyond that, I think everybody here -- you and I --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 299991.0,
      "end_time": 302178.0,
      "text": "we have a role to play in that."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 302202.0,
      "end_time": 304495.0,
      "text": "We are the ones who share the content."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 304519.0,
      "end_time": 307300.0,
      "text": "We are the ones who share the stories online."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 307540.0,
      "end_time": 309241.0,
      "text": "In this day and age, we&#39;re all publishers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 310355.0,
      "end_time": 312846.0,
      "text": "and we have responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 312870.0,
      "end_time": 315180.0,
      "text": "In my job as a journalist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 315204.0,
      "end_time": 317232.0,
      "text": "I check, I verify."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 317256.0,
      "end_time": 320537.0,
      "text": "I trust my gut, but I ask tough questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 321440.0,
      "end_time": 324316.0,
      "text": "Why is this person telling me this story?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 324340.0,
      "end_time": 327839.0,
      "text": "What do they have to gain by sharing this information?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 327863.0,
      "end_time": 329671.0,
      "text": "Do they have a hidden agenda?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 330502.0,
      "end_time": 335993.0,
      "text": "I really believe that we must all start to ask tougher questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 336170.0,
      "end_time": 338327.0,
      "text": "of information that we discover online."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 341493.0,
      "end_time": 347224.0,
      "text": "Research shows that some of us don&#39;t even read beyond headlines"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 347248.0,
      "end_time": 349351.0,
      "text": "before we share stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 349375.0,
      "end_time": 350914.0,
      "text": "Who here has done that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 351764.0,
      "end_time": 353990.0,
      "text": "I know I have."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 354255.0,
      "end_time": 355614.0,
      "text": "But what if"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 357115.0,
      "end_time": 361324.0,
      "text": "we stopped taking information that we discover at face value?"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 362700.0,
      "end_time": 365643.0,
      "text": "What if we stop to think about the consequence"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 365667.0,
      "end_time": 368116.0,
      "text": "of the information that we pass on"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 368140.0,
      "end_time": 371351.0,
      "text": "and its potential to incite violence or hatred?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 372415.0,
      "end_time": 376950.0,
      "text": "What if we stop to think about the real-life consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 376974.0,
      "end_time": 378822.0,
      "text": "of the information that we share?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 379925.0,
      "end_time": 381725.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much for listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 381749.0,
      "end_time": 385243.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}